body:
HypixelOverlay is a client-side fabric mod to provide players with a quick way to view player statistics directly within the game, without the need to tab out or use external websites.

## How to Use
- Get your hypixel api key from [Hypixel Developer Dashboard](https://developer.hypixel.net/dashboard/)
- Enter the key in the config (can be opened by pressing the Open Config keybind, defaults to 'I') and close it with ESC.
- Press the Refresh Stats keybind (defaults to 'O') to get stats of players in your current game.
- Now you can see the stats at the right of your chat.

## Which statistics are visible?
In all gamemodes, the Network Level is visible. The following stats are for specific games:
### BedWars
- BedWars Level (Stars);
- Winsteak;
- FKDR (Final Kill-Death Ratio);
- WLR (Win-Loss Ratio);
- Final Kills;
- Wins;
- Beds Destroyed;

## Limitations
- The mod only works while connected to hypixel.net
- The mod was made to only view bedwars stats, other gamemodes might be added sometime.
